flowRoot.flowPara: To style to your links like those above youll need to edit the HTML files and the CSS file.
In each of your HTML files remove the one link from the menu that leads to same page.
For example, in the about-me.html page you will remove the <a href="about-me.html"> link, in the books.html page you will remove the <a href="books.html"> link.
links appear light blue and underlined when you hover over them
current page is yellow and clickable
Do this for all the files in your site (for example family.html and pets.html).
Notice that after you make this change the menu entry is no longer clickable.
